Getting Started
Follow these instructions to set up and run the Snake game on your local machine.

Prerequisites
Python: Ensure Python is installed on your system. You can download it from python.org.
Pygame: This game uses the Pygame library for graphical display.

Install Dependencies:
Ensure you have Pygame installed. You can install it using pip: "pip install pygame".

Run the Game:
Execute the following command to start the game: "python snake_game.py".
Use the arrow keys to control the snake.
